# Festag — no kicker labels

Do **not** use uppercase/meta “kicker” or eyebrow labels above titles in Festag UI.

Bad:
- `Anmeldung` above a login headline
- `Chrome-Erweiterung` above a section title
- `Entscheidung` / `Workspace` / `Hilfe` as small caps meta lines

Prefer:
- Go straight to the **title** (and optional subtitle/body)
- Section headings as normal-weight titles (`h2`/`h3`), not uppercase kickers
- Context in the title or a calm subtitle — not a separate eyebrow

`EmptyState` already ignores deprecated `kicker` props. Do not reintroduce visible `.*-kicker` eyebrow patterns on new surfaces.

When touching existing UI, strip leftover kicker elements and their CSS.
